    <h1>About CareSphere</h1>
    <p>Welcome to CareSphere, a beacon of wellness located on MG Road in the vibrant city of Mangalore. At CareSphere, we are devoted to providing exceptional healthcare services with a personal touch. Our commitment to your well-being is at the core of everything we do.</p>

    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>At CareSphere, our mission is to foster a healthier Mangalore by delivering compassionate and comprehensive healthcare services. We strive to create an environment where patients feel valued, supported, and confident in their journey towards optimal health.</p>

